text: Fred Wiedersporn (19 October 1931 - 8 January 2016) was a German gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics, representing Saar. ==See also== * Saar at the 1952 Summer Olympics ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2016 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Saar Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Saarlouis (district)
